total_jobs.description: total number of jobs run for group

unmatched_percent.description: total unmatched divided by total count

unmatched.description: number of unmatched jobs that could not be assigned a cluster by rainbow

build_success.description: reflects if the package had exactly what it needed for a successful build

marginal_score.description: if partial points were given for getting some dependency versions right

versions_in_range.description: total points earned vs. total points possible, where 1 point means a correct version in a range

matched_clusters_per_job.description: number of clusters rainbow deemed a match based on version ranges and compatibility metadata provided
